description:
It was discovered that Python incorrectly handled certain inputs.
An attacker could possibly use this issue to execute arbitrary code.
title: Python vulnerability
summary: python2.7, python3.10, python3.4, python3.5, python3.6, python3.8, python3.9 vulnerability
action: In general, a standard system update will make all the necessary changes.
isummary:
Python could be made to run arbitrary code if it received a specially
crafted input.
